{"tid":1571802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我！以！後！唔！會！再！懶！型！","createTime":"2019-09-15T13:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T16:07:40.000Z","uid":314462,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"430394e4102b6735e7f54c3f1c5b6751f4b779e8","tid":1571802,"uid":314462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:58:43.000Z","msg":"話說今日夢見自己想係馬路跳欄過翻去行人路入面。咁跳啦，我左手一撐，右手揸住把姐嘅，一跳就唸住一次過可以雙腳跳過去，點知發覺好似差少少，隻腳一縮跟住戟親個欄踩唔穩，得隻左腳過到去，成個人差啲錫到地下，仆曬街，右腳上下三吋果個位撞魚咗好腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n一起翻身即9秒9跑走，唔想比人見到我咁染，沿途聽到一句話：師兄你下次可以唔洗咁型嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路跑果陣都好似比人恥笑緊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發誓唔會再有同類事情發生！操fit自己做足準備功夫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"673bf0e7c28401a3168fe25e8d46695f0b5bc9cb","tid":1571802,"uid":248333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bf386fc0390352ab14bb0be70aa9a39269849a","tid":1571802,"uid":237417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:00:34.000Z","msg":"柒"},{"pid":"bbd9167e6d55b9f0722af6b9870ca6cc4364a0a0","tid":1571802,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"失敗乃成功之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}